A sweet-scented top note opens with a delectable top note that blends light and elegant bergamot zesty and fresh blackcurrant leaves with spirited notes of pineapple. This flows into the heart note which is a charming mix of soft mimosa extracts strong and green hints of apple blossom and floral notes of lotus. It finishes off with a rich and warming base note with heavy yet soothing hints of musk woody cedar and creamy vanilla. A diverse range of fragrant extracts that make up this floral fruity fragrance add an extra dose of zing to your carefree mornings. The bottle that encases this vibrant scent comes in the characteristic style of Police Pure series with a rounded shell structure. Vividly painted strokes of hot pink against stark white form the Statue of Liberty the symbol of the most popular cosmopolitan city - New York. The sharp and contrasting colours are symbolic of the urbane and provocative woman who would saunter down the streets of this dynamic city. With a dab of Police New York get ready to amaze and conquer.

Vivacious yet subtle this luxury scent spins a tale of a faraway land covered in serene clouds and a magical journey. For the woman with wings on her feet an eternal slave of wanderlust Police Wings transports her to the unventured territories she has always dreamed of. Created by Domitille Bertier this Eau de Toilette that exudes a beguiling enamor is made for the distinguished brand of Police.

The cheerful top note opens with fruity hints of red currant tart hints of blackcurrant and a ripe accord of pear that seams it together. Moving into the heart you can take in the fragrant heart note that is dominated by the floral freshness of sweet hints of rose light notes of iris and distinctly feminine peony extracts. The base note dries down with a classic combination of creamy vanilla soothing and heavy notes of musk along with rich sandalwood. The lively and vibrant hints of fresh and natural ingredients make up a delectable fresh floral fragrance that folds you in a summery mist any time you choose to wear it. This refreshing fragrance comes enclosed in a tall and slender dual-toned glass bottle with a slight curve at the center. The base of the vial flaunts a glowing transparency that steadily turns ink-blue from the neck upwards. A whiff of this chic and velvety perfume and take off into a mystical land of unknown possibilities.
